8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 10=

11
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:58,079
Thank... thank you.

12
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:01,600
I'm a princess from Xichu,

13
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:02,880
just like you,

14
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,280
living here for now.

15
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:05,920
So...

16
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:09,239
We're both homeless here.

17
00:01:12,079 --> 00:01:14,480
Tears are the most useless thing.

18
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,959
They won't buy you sympathy.

19
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:18,439
They only make you look weak
and easy to bully.

20
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:21,000
If you don't want to be trampled,

21
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:23,239
you need to grow your own fangs.

22
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:45,840
Princess Anhe...

23
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:52,200
Prince Xuanlie embezzled
400,000 taels of border funds

24
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:54,920
to breed Deathsworns
in the capital's outskirts.

25
00:01:55,439 --> 00:01:57,079
This is beyond reckless.

26
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,439
Practically treason.

27
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,840
Not enough yet.

28
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,120
Keep gathering evidence.

29
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:13,039
This won't make Father
intent on killing him.

30
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:15,319
If we expose this now,

31
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,439
we will only alert him.

32
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,759
I'm on it.

33
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,199
May you recover soon, Your Highness,

34
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:24,319
and take control again.

35
00:02:34,159 --> 00:02:35,599
It's to clear residual toxins.

36
00:02:35,759 --> 00:02:36,719
Drink it.

37
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,439
Jian,

38
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:42,800
I've agreed to be
Prince Xuanlie's Secondary Consort.

39
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,520
On the wedding day,

40
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:45,800
his guard will drop.

41
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:49,439
That's when I'll send him to his death.

42
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,159
All right.

43
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:57,639
Then I'll prepare your escape route.

44
00:02:58,960 --> 00:02:59,560
By the way,

45
00:02:59,759 --> 00:03:03,080
Prince Jinghe's been
smashing things lately,

46
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:03,879
losing his temper.

47
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,080
What exactly happened that day?

48
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:08,840
Nothing.

49
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,960
Before that,

50
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:19,080
I want to say goodbye to Murong Jinghe.

51
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:37,199
Let me help you up.

52
00:03:37,319 --> 00:03:38,520
I don't need your pity!

53
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,199
Your Highness,

54
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,719
I just want to help.

55
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,800
I don't need it.

56
00:04:05,439 --> 00:04:06,240
Get out.

57
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:16,360
Okay.

58
00:04:23,759 --> 00:04:24,560
Just go.

59
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,279
Such pain isn't so bad.

60
00:04:54,759 --> 00:04:55,560
Mei Lin,

61
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:58,439
you entered this palace
only for revenge.

62
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:00,680
Don't fall for temptation.

63
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,879
They bullied you as well.

64
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,000
I never thought

65
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:11,720
we'd both be trapped

66
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,839
in this dark, lightless palace,

67
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:15,560
struggling to survive.

68
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:17,920
Come on.

69
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:21,000
(Flower Viewing Feast)
Cheers.

70
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,800
(Flower Viewing Feast)
Great wine here.

71
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:25,199
It's rare to gather
with all my sons today.

72
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,680
No need to be formal.

73
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:27,959
Feel free to talk.

74
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:28,879
Good.

75
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:29,680
Sure.

76
00:05:30,199 --> 00:05:32,360
Father, I have a request.

77
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,519
Princess Anhe is a woman of grace.

78
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,839
She's captured my heart.

79
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:39,279
I beg you to grant Mei Lin
as my secondary consort.

80
00:05:53,319 --> 00:05:54,759
Your Majesty, I...

81
00:05:54,759 --> 00:05:55,560
Father,

82
00:05:57,319 --> 00:06:00,040
you conferred Princess Anhe
personally before.

83
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:02,079
She deserves more than that.

84
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,199
I...

85
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:12,319
also fancy Princess Anhe.

86
00:06:15,879 --> 00:06:17,720
I beg you to grant her to me

87
00:06:17,959 --> 00:06:20,560
as my principal consort.

88
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,600
Luomei,

89
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,839
what do you think?

90
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,920
Your Majesty, Prince Xuanlie and I
grew up together.

91
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,879
We're devoted.

92
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,519
I'm also very fond of Princess Anhe.

93
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,319
I'd be glad to share
Prince Xuanlie with her

94
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,000
and serve him together.

95
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:48,959
Your Majesty, Prince Xuanlie
is the future Crown Prince.

96
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,879
His inner court matters a lot.

97
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:53,959
If Princess Anhe is made
his secondary consort,

98
00:06:54,319 --> 00:06:56,439
it will both satisfy
Prince Xuanlie's wish

99
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,560
and appease
the remaining forces of Xichu.

100
00:06:59,079 --> 00:07:00,439
As for Prince Jinghe,

101
00:07:00,439 --> 00:07:01,560
his health is weak.

102
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,720
He needs a strong

103
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:06,079
and capable wife by his side.

104
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:09,199
General Muye's family
has bred generals for generations,

105
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:10,399
brave and skilled in battle.

106
00:07:10,879 --> 00:07:12,560
If Luomei is betrothed to him,

107
00:07:13,879 --> 00:07:15,160
it could also provide our family

108
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:17,199
with some strong and capable offspring.

109
00:07:19,279 --> 00:07:21,920
My dear, that's a great idea.

110
00:07:22,959 --> 00:07:23,839
By my decree:

111
00:07:24,439 --> 00:07:26,040
Princess Anhe, Mei Lin,

112
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:28,800
is betrothed to Prince Murong Xuanlie.

113
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:31,240
General Muye Luomei

114
00:07:31,519 --> 00:07:33,680
is betrothed to Prince Murong Jinghe.

115
